public interface Task

Represent a download/upload task

  • 方法详细资料

    • fromUri

      static Task fromUri​(java.net.URI uri)
      Construct a task from the given uri
      参数:
      uri - the uri used to construct task
      返回:
      the constructed task
      抛出:
      UnsupportedProtocolException - if the given protocol is not supported
      java.lang.NullPointerException - if the given uri is null

    • fromFile

      static Task fromFile​(java.io.File file)
      Construct a task from the given file
      参数:
      file - the file used to construct task
      返回:
      the constructed task
      抛出:
      UnsupportedProtocolException - if the protocol is not supported
      java.lang.NullPointerException - if the given file is null
      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the given is not a file, such as a directory

    • status

      Task.Status status()
      Get the current task status
      返回:
      the current status

    • start

      void start()
      Change the status to WAITING, the task will be executed once possible
      抛出:
      java.lang.IllegalStateException - if the task is not in WAITING status

    • pause

      void pause()
      Change the status to PAUSED, can be restarted via start
      抛出:
      java.lang.IllegalStateException - if the task is not in ACTIVE or WAITING status

    • stop

      void stop()
      Change the status to STOPPED, the task is not restartable after that

      Get the download speed, in bytes/second

      the download speed
